WEBVTT

00:00:00.988 --> 00:00:03.194
Da vam ispričam jednu priču.

00:00:03.194 --> 00:00:05.103
Ona nas vraća
200 miliona godina unazad.

00:00:05.103 --> 00:00:07.087
To je priča o neokorteksu,

00:00:07.087 --> 00:00:09.061
što znači "nova kora".

00:00:09.061 --> 00:00:11.492
Kod ranih sisara,

00:00:11.492 --> 00:00:13.547
jer jedino sisari imaju neokorteks,

00:00:13.547 --> 00:00:15.211
stvorenja nalik glodarima,

00:00:15.211 --> 00:00:18.790
bio je veličine poštanske markice
i isto tako tanak.

00:00:18.790 --> 00:00:20.229
Bio je tanki omotač

00:00:20.229 --> 00:00:22.493
oko njihovog mozga veličine oraha,

00:00:22.493 --> 00:00:25.944
ali je bio sposoban
za novu vrstu razmišljanja.

00:00:25.944 --> 00:00:27.761
Za razliku od utvrđenih ponašanja

00:00:27.761 --> 00:00:29.753
koje imaju ne-sisari,

00:00:29.753 --> 00:00:32.445
on je mogao da smisli nova ponašanja.